Let me share my road map in learning deep learning here
1. Python 
2. Ml basics
3. Linear regression
4. loss functions
5. Optimizer
6. Explore tensorflow or pytorch
7. Explore loss functions, optimizer, no.of hidden layers with inbuilt datasets or small dataset
8. Explore both regression and  classification problems
9. Learn to hyperparameter tune
10. Image preprocessing
11. Opencv or pillow
12. CNN basics
13. Architectures(lenet, alexnet,vgg16,19, inception v1,v2,v3, resnet,mobilenet,)
14. Repeat step 7,9
15. Projects
16. Object detection basics
17. Classical computer vision
18. Modern day computer vision need
19. RCNN 
20. RCNN family
21. Project with rcnn family 
22. Yolo and its varies
23. Project with yolo family
24. Detectron 
25. Project with detectron.
26. SSD
27. project with ssd
